Non-Contentious Construction Associate 3PQE, Dubai
Non-Contentious Construction Associate 3PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This well-established international law firm has one of the region’s largest and most highly regarded construction practices. The firm is now seeking to recruit a non-contentious construction associate to join the team in Dubai.
The ideal candidate will be 3PQE, qualified in the UK, Australia or New Zealand and have experience in mainly front-end work from a recognised law firm with a strong presence in the field of mainstream construction. Candidates with a mix contentious and non-contentious background will also be considered. Regional experience whilst preferable is not mandatory. You will be driven, enthusiastic and a team player with a genuine interest in marketing and relationship building.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
